reviewText: I don't think I've ever had such high hopes for a movie and been so totally disappointed once I started watching. They had the chance to give so many great camera views of the women naked and they  just totally pissed it away. One woman is topless. Two women give full frontals. One of them is a brief up close.
I agree with the other reviewer, Brigitte Lahaie does make this worth it.
Good looking DVD. Brigitte Lahaie makes this movie worthwhile.
